data.description: ESCROW FALL OUT AS OF 12/02/2023 GORGEOUS COMPLETELY REMODELED HOME LOCATED WITHIN BLOCKS FROM MISSION LAKES COUNTRY CLUB AND JUST MINUTES AWAY FROM THE PALM SPRINGS AERIAL TRAMWAY, THE DESERT MUSEUM, ART GALLERIES, THEATERS, RESTAURANTS AND SHOPPING.  RENOVATION INCLUDES NEW WOOD VENEER FLOORS ** NEW BASEBOARD ** NEW WHITE SHAKER KITCHEN CABINETS ** GRANITE COUNTERTOPS ** FRESH PAINT INSIDE AND OUT ** NEW VANITIES IN BOTH BATHROOMS WITH ALL NEW CUSTOM SHOWERS ** NEWER WATER HEATER.  IN ADDITION THIS HOME OFFERS EXTRA STORAGE SPACE IN THE GARAGE AS WELL AS CENTRAL HEATING AND AIR CONDITIONING.  SELLER TO INSTALL NEW STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES  WHICH INCLUDES STOVE, MICROWAVE, AND DISHWASHER AT CLOSE OF ESCROW.  HURRY ALL INTERESTED BUYERS THIS HOME IS A HOT BUY AND WON'T LAST LONG ON THE MARKET!!!
